00:12:03.523 --> 00:12:05.440 align:middle line:84%
than to go out there and
then change and build

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:08.230 align:middle line:84%
a whole new world, because
just by changing consciousness,

00:12:08.230 --> 00:12:09.400 align:middle line:90%
a new world will manifest.

00:12:09.400 --> 00:12:11.440 align:middle line:84%
So to me, that's a
really important one,

00:12:11.440 --> 00:12:13.090 align:middle line:84%
because quantum
physics not only brings

00:12:13.090 --> 00:12:15.080 align:middle line:84%
in mind and consciousness
as a source,

00:12:15.080 --> 00:12:17.530 align:middle line:84%
but it also says there's no
such thing as separation,

00:12:17.530 --> 00:12:19.770 align:middle line:84%
which is what Newtonian
physics always talked about.

00:12:19.770 --> 00:12:20.950 align:middle line:90%
I can separate the pieces.

00:12:20.950 --> 00:12:23.710 align:middle line:84%
But quantum physics says
everything is energy.

00:12:23.710 --> 00:12:25.150 align:middle line:90%
Everything's entangled.

00:12:25.150 --> 00:12:27.700 align:middle line:84%
And this becomes important,
because we created a world

00:12:27.700 --> 00:12:29.350 align:middle line:90%
based on separation.

00:12:29.350 --> 00:12:32.470 align:middle line:84%
And that separation
is so out of alignment

00:12:32.470 --> 00:12:36.040 align:middle line:84%
