00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:38.320 align:middle line:84%
is to bring back
harmony and community.

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:41.860 align:middle line:84%
So part of the chaos, and
you see the breaking down

00:12:41.860 --> 00:12:44.590 align:middle line:84%
