00:13:22.430 --> 00:13:25.958 align:middle line:84%
The change is what we need
to survive on this planet.

00:13:25.958 --> 00:13:27.250 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: Well, I agree, Bruce.

00:13:27.250 --> 00:13:30.340 align:middle line:84%
And I think this is where the
