00:13:50.620 --> 00:13:52.190 align:middle line:90%
And I think that's important.

00:13:52.190 --> 00:13:53.740 align:middle line:90%
>>LIPTON: I agree with this.

00:13:53.740 --> 00:13:57.970 align:middle line:84%
It's so important to recognize
that what's happening

00:13:57.970 --> 00:14:02.800 align:middle line:84%
is so positive in the face
of what looks so negative.

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:04.660 align:middle line:90%
But knowledge is power.

00:14:04.660 --> 00:14:07.780 align:middle line:84%
