00:14:20.500 --> 00:14:23.290 align:middle line:84%
Because with this new
science comes some very

00:14:23.290 --> 00:14:25.540 align:middle line:84%
profound knowledge,
and that also

00:14:25.540 --> 00:14:27.820 align:middle line:90%
means very profound empowerment.

00:14:27.820 --> 00:14:31.030 align:middle line:84%
And this is what is the
drive force of evolution--

00:14:31.030 --> 00:14:32.502 align:middle line:90%
consciousness, as you mentioned.

00:14:32.502 --> 00:14:34.960 align:middle line:84%
Which is completely different
than the conventional science

00:14:34.960 --> 00:14:38.920 align:middle line:84%
that has always said genes are
the foundation of evolution.

00:14:38.920 --> 00:14:42.250 align:middle line:84%
It turns out after the Human
Genome Project, the whole idea

00:14:42.250 --> 00:14:45.580 align:middle line:84%
