crash, because humans

00:14:45.580 --> 00:14:47.350 align:middle line:84%
have about 20,000
genes, which is

00:14:47.350 --> 00:14:50.230 align:middle line:84%
the same number of genes
in a half millimeter

00:14:50.230 --> 00:14:51.910 align:middle line:90%
worm that has 1,200 cells.

00:14:51.910 --> 00:14:54.460 align:middle line:90%
We've got 50 trillion cells.

00:14:54.460 --> 00:14:57.400 align:middle line:84%
The worm has 1,271
cells, and we both

00:14:57.400 --> 00:14:59.000 align:middle line:90%
have the same number of genes.

00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:00.790 align:middle line:84%
So basically, it
says, well, then I

00:15:00.790 --> 00:15:02.790 align:middle line:84%
can't score human
evolution on genes.

00:15:02.790 --> 00:15:05.020 align:middle line:84%
We've got the same
number as the worm.

00:15:05.020 --> 00:15:08.380 align:middle line:84%
So it turns out consciousness--
and this is really

00:15:08.380 --> 00:15:11.350 align:middle line:84%
the important part,
because consciousness,

00:15:11.350 --> 00:15:13.742 align:middle line:84%
we are free to create
our consciousness.

00:15:13.742 --> 00:15:15.700 align:middle line:84%
And if we are free to
create our consciousness,

00:15:15.700 --> 00:15:18.700 align:middle line:90%
then we are powerful creators.

00:15:18.700 --> 00:15:21.250 align:middle line:84%
But we have to give
information, because most people

00:15:21.250 --> 00:15:22.950 align:middle line:90%
feel they're victims.

00:15:22.950 --> 00:15:26.830 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: You know, there
is a new way of thinking

00:15:26.830 --> 00:15:30.170 align:middle line:84%
